Stock analyzer tool

The goal of this project is to create an easy to use interface for analyzing stocks.
It is an ongoing project, which I plan to update regularly with different data
science and statistical methodologies to understand stock price movement. 
Plan
  sentiment analysis using NLP techniques
  time series analysis( different moving averages, etc)
  correlation to economic indicators
  correlation to competitors or indexes
  Black-Scholes option pricing model?
  
